user: I think I'll try adding a pinch of vanilla powder to the creamer to give it a classic flavor boost. I've heard that vanilla and French roast are a great combination. Do you have any suggestions on how to incorporate the vanilla powder into the creamer? Should I mix it in before or after brewing the coffee?
